title: Stylized Flower
description: An illustration of a stylized flower with two elongated, orange petals at the top, resembling a pair of lips or a seed pod. The petals are open, revealing small, round seeds inside. The flower is supported by a long, green stem, and there are tiny yellow particles appearing to fall from the flower, suggesting the dispersal of seeds.

title: Yellow Lily Flower
description: A vibrant illustration of a yellow lily flower, featuring broad, wavy petals that radiate outward. The center of the flower showcases green and red reproductive structures, including stamens and a pistil, set against the bright yellow petals.

title: Flowering Plant Close-Up
